		<credit project="CfPBoK@https://slebok.github.io/cfpbok/"/>
		<h1>Tag <code>T2E</code>: Documentation</h1>
		Work where documentation or knowledge transfer is central: language documentation practices, literate specifications, pedagogical artefacts tightly coupled to a language, and documentation-driven engineering such as deriving software artefacts from docs/specs. Broader narratives around teaching or experience can be secondary <a href="t6a.html">T6A</a>.
